  abstract    =	{All analytical and simulation research on ad~hoc wireless
		networks must necessarily model radio propagation using
		simplifying assumptions. We provide a comprehensive review of
		six assumptions that are still part of many ad~hoc network
		simulation studies, despite increasing awareness of the need
