  keyword     =	{Sensor Networks, Sensor Deployment, ZebraNet, GPS},
  abstract    =	{ The enormous potential for wireless sensor networks to make
		a positive impact on our society has spawned a great deal of
		research on the topic, and this research is now producing
		environment-ready systems. Current technology limits coupled
		with widely-varying application requirements lead to a
		diversity of hardware platforms for diÂ®erent portions of the
